        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued August 4 at 5:21PM MDT until August 4 at 6:00PM MDT by NWS Rapid City SD</headline>
        <description>At 521 PM MDT, a severe thunderstorm was located over Rumford, or 14
miles southeast of Edgemont, moving northeast at 20 mph.

HAZARD...Ping pong ball size hail and 60 mph wind gusts.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...People and animals outdoors will be injured. Expect hail
damage to roofs, siding, windows, and vehicles. Expect wind
damage to roofs, siding, and trees.

Locations impacted include...
Rumford.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
